Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.96,0:00:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.17,0:00:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.38,0:00:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.59,0:00:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.18,0:00:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是親愛的 晶子 親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.68,0:00:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了嘛？阿晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.73,0:00:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.19,0:00:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下不了手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.73,0:00:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請...請你原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.42,0:01:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像還在作夢一樣 溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.55,0:01:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然還能夠跟爸爸媽媽一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.55,0:01:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣三個人一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.93,0:01:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得幸福嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.39,0:01:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切都是因為有溫子的幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.23,0:01:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.24,0:01:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣幸福的日子能夠持續多久呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.18,0:03:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.51,0:03:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作為什麼要這樣做呢？到底是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.52,0:03:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在叫人難以相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這已經成為事實了 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.78,0:03:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這種結果也是我原本就希望的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.62,0:03:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個堂堂的女高中生機器人居然會向人低頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人他們到底在說些什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼隨便的就答應別人的約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家一叫就馬上出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.72,0:03:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有很重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.93,0:04:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就去打聽一下怎麼樣啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.56,0:04:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.98,0:04:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 拿著這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是附有吸盤的手套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是很希望能夠和龍之介一起生活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.45,0:04:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.74,0:04:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目晶子 說一就是一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.41,0:04:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我有一個交換絛件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.04,0:04:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交換條件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.25,0:04:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.26,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在太困難了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.43,0:04:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...交換條件是什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.14,0:04:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是自古以來永恆不變的母愛溫暖 還有媽媽的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介目前最需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.85,0:04:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸曾經說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.65,0:04:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你要我怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你...好好的善待他就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要達抗你的先生哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.44,0:04:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括做飯、洗衣服、婦除等工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.53,0:05:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要由你自己來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.16,0:05:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莉莎 現在我要開始竊聽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.12,0:05:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.17,0:05:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在太可惡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.60,0:05:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這種無聊條件 你想會輕易的答應嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.65,0:05:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像做飯、洗衣服這麼鎖碎的事叫傭人做就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這樣的人我會去做嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.45,0:05:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸跟媽媽能夠和好 一家三口快樂的生活在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是龍之介最希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.38,0:05:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為能待在孩子身邊陪伴他就是母愛的一種表達方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.01,0:06:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.85,0:06:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能夠愛龍之介的話 我拜託你答應好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和龍之介在一起生活也可以說是我長久以來的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 這個條件我接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.36,0:06:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.28,0:06:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最後的那一招 我可不認為是很人道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.42,0:06:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我跟爸爸跟溫子三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.80,0:06:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起搬進了媽媽的三島的老家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.26,0:06:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這樣是不是太過份了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.27,0:06:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日本這種事情叫做一家團圓 不會很過份的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.90,0:07:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好像是一篇長篇小說一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.74,0:07:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃早餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照常理來說 那邊是牆壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對這邊的人來說要從這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃早餐囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.29,0:07:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等得真的很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.96,0:07:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快點來吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.84,0:07:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說殺魚要殺的乾淨俐落嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.18,0:07:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事...不是應該...要你去...去做的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.23,0:07:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有納豆上面不加蕃茄醬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你看 白飯是煮熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.94,0:07:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過怎麼好像有一點酸酸的檸檬味呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米你洗過了沒有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.03,0:07:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用媽咪牌神檬洗潔精洗得很乾淨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼把故意約定的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做的和原來的意思完全相反呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是這個意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是太讓我失望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.42,0:07:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何一件事情是成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.13,0:08:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣的飯怎麼可以吃呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為一個母親你實在是太失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸你別這麼說嘛 先吃吃看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.09,0:08:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒覺得挺好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.81,0:08:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽做的菜不錯哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.60,0:08:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個肉真的很香很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 你吃吃看嘛 很好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.94,0:08:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個肉是我做的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.28,0:08:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這...怎麼會變成這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.41,0:08:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這...這真是故鄉的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.00,0:08:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個...這個就是媽媽的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.01,0:08:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.72,0:08:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這個樣子的阿晶小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不像原來的阿晶小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情到了這個地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.18,0:08:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只好使用暴力將少爺搶過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.44,0:08:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.35,0:09:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果現在這個樣子的生活是龍之介希望的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.73,0:09:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.61,0:09:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一樣東西我要讓你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.71,0:09:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.50,0:09:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是葛雷姆兩千最新的原型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.00,0:09:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經完成了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.13,0:09:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.00,0:09:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經輸入了能夠分析溫子所有運動能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.59,0:09:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟一切行動方向的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.47,0:09:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要的 這組織系統都能夠幫你處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要小姐你一聲命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.01,0:09:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時都可以把那個多事的貓娘給...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前為止 你都一直讓他們玩弄著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.81,0:09:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你就繼續讓他們這樣下去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.16,0:10:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 現在我要去洗衣服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.67,0:10:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗衣服 洗衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.17,0:10:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.35,0:10:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麽事情啊？曾爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.40,0:10:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.07,0:10:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是覺得很高興 龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.99,0:10:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不可以再像剛才那樣叫我一次？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.16,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾爺…爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.79,0:10:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.29,0:10:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛剛明明叫的很順的 再叫一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.21,0:10:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾爺爺 怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.01,0:10:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你們看個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是軍事機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.94,0:11:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們說用它來玩一場戰爭進戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.66,0:11:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子的話它太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.74,0:11:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？可是可能很有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們用這個傢伙來玩相撲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...玩什麽好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.84,0:11:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降落傘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降...降落...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.01,0:11:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.55,0:11:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來玩那個叫降落的遊戲吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.31,0:11:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鴨子的媽媽洗衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗呀…洗呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.86,0:11:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.86,0:11:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒哦 曾爺爺好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒哦 好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子 再快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.62,0:12:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.04,0:12:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等 這樣太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.61,0:12:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.24,0:12:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鴨子的媽媽洗衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.91,0:12:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗呀…洗呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.91,0:12:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鴨子的媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.79,0:12:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.59,0:12:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福像一瞬間冬天的太陽嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.30,0:13:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早點抓到的話或許會更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.32,0:13:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天這樣不停的做家事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.74,0:13:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連陪伴龍之介玩耍的時間都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.37,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.20,0:13:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那媽媽跟龍之介一起生活 就失去它的意義了不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子 這只是一種考驗而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.89,0:13:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本個性就任性又高傲的阿晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.72,0:13:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一次是她有生以第一次為自己所愛的人犧牲呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果阿晶一旦通過了這次考驗的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.23,0:13:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她勢必會變得更成熟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.40,0:13:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶子如果心中有愛的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了嗎 溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.49,0:14:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.16,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你之所以會這麼做 原來是為了她好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你會認為晶子很可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.42,0:14:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就表示你也變成一個善解人意的女孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.69,0:14:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很欣賞小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.19,0:14:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不但有氣質而且清新高貴 人又長得美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.40,0:14:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從前 對男人橫行霸道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.49,0:14:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是現在的小姐已經完全變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.20,0:14:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成了男人的應聲蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.53,0:14:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這自尊心和身份地位也沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.54,0:14:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不忍心看到...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不忍心看到她這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.88,0:14:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了 小姐 你多多保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的阿莉莎敬上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.01,0:15:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你不能了解我所做的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.56,0:15:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不過是想和龍之介一起生活而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,況且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請容我再說一句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.48,0:15:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為小姐的時間已經被家事填滿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.28,0:15:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一來就永遠沒有時間跟龍之介少爺相處在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 對小姐而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.82,0:15:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在跟以前分開住的時候根本沒有差別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.20,0:15:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就是完全一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.83,0:15:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前分開住的時候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.09,0:15:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前分開住的時候完全一樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜牲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.27,0:15:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然連我夏目晶子你也敢戲弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.90,0:16:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.21,0:16:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.80,0:16:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 還要接住這一球哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.55,0:16:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.80,0:16:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾爺爺 龍之介 快點離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.39,0:16:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.85,0:16:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.98,0:16:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.37,0:16:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們公司的新型機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.66,0:16:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葛雷姆兩千
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.83,0:16:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.08,0:17:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然勾結久作一起來戲弄我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.59,0:17:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個恥辱我一定會一百萬倍的還給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.43,0:17:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了 貓娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.72,0:17:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 等一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.72,0:17:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.48,0:17:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個誤會嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.02,0:17:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要這樣子啦 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.98,0:17:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要這個樣子好不好嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.19,0:17:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麽不能像以前一樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.37,0:17:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做的菜越來越好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.99,0:17:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你整理過我的房間也感覺特別的溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.46,0:17:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你洗過的衣服有一股特別的香味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.38,0:17:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論是哪個地方都充滿了媽媽你的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.09,0:17:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些都是自從我跟媽媽生活在一起之後才體會得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.80,0:17:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是因為溫子的幫忙我們現在才能夠住在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.85,0:17:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而現在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.85,0:17:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然把溫子當作仇人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.02,0:18:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽你現在這個樣子 我討厭你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.45,0:18:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.03,0:18:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介討厭媽媽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.42,0:18:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽雖然你 可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.38,0:18:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽不能放棄自己的原則來討你的歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實 在這一個月裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就不像原來的自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.81,0:18:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為為了你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.19,0:18:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了要遵守和溫子和久作之間的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.61,0:18:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才偽裝起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我要恢復原來的樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.03,0:18:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.13,0:18:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.15,0:18:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和你挑戰 我要帶走龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.45,0:18:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我將用我原來的面目來疼愛龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開 龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.50,0:19:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了 貓娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.21,0:19:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要以母愛的名義向你桃戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招！發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.93,0:19:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一天終究還是來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.02,0:19:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要想個辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.63,0:19:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你接招吧 母愛的飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.84,0:19:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.06,0:20:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.60,0:20:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.99,0:20:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的心情我也不是不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.16,0:20:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.83,0:20:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓她去吧 等她氣消了就沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.75,0:20:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正家裡鬧鬧 別人不會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.13,0:20:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要東跑西跑的躲來躲去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.72,0:20:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來跟我面對面的作戰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.39,0:20:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是媽媽 這種事我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有辦法做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.06,0:20:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,納命吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.23,0:20:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.32,0:20:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是專為了你 還特別去調整過的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.53,0:20:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子 接著這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.29,0:21:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.93,0:21:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子 不要考慮這麼多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.10,0:21:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點把這個拿著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是專為了配合你 而製造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.56,0:21:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說除了溫子 沒有任何人可以使用它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.27,0:21:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再做讓媽媽受傷害的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常把你看成人類一樣的管教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.78,0:21:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦到了緊要關頭就使喚你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.12,0:21:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.54,0:21:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是爲了預防萬一而製造的特製溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.34,0:21:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做”迷你溫子”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.17,0:21:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作 你這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.47,0:22:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又來搗蛋 妨礙我辦正事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.48,0:22:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.90,0:22:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.73,0:22:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.52,0:22:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.53,0:22:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一次 每一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.24,0:22:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在緊要關頭的時候 你都來破壞我的事我要你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.81,0:22:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.77,0:22:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是用來對付無機物的兵器 對人類是沒有害處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.53,0:22:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.86,0:23:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.20,0:23:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於現出原形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.74,0:23:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧 久作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.87,0:23:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 阿晶住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.54,0:23:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.54,0:23:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.05,0:23:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們去吧 溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.26,0:23:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.72,0:23:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們兩個和那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.89,0:23:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.01,0:23:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.06,0:23:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在發現耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.44,0:23:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸也是 媽媽也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.90,0:23:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.11,0:23:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛情真是一個很奇妙的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.00,0:23:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.87,0:23:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.30,0:24:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.30,0:24:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介快點起來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.14,0:24:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天又要開始了呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.10,0:24:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐讓我等一下再吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.27,0:24:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家還沒被弄壞之前趕快去學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.11,0:24:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉告久作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.49,0:24:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把龍之介交出來 乖乖的投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.03,0:24:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不交出來的話 我就要攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.12,0:24:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都來這麼一次 怎麼會不煩呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.79,0:24:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.54,0:24:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶子我告訴你 你老實點認輸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.80,0:24:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 他出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.38,0:24:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！結束了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.19,0:25:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就是這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.49,0:25:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們每天還是快樂地生活在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.08,0:25:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.50,0:00:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
